entries.journal_entry_description: The Sand People are rampaging due to your theft of their relics. They are slaughtering everyone in Mos Espa. You must stop them.
entries.journal_entry_title: Tusken Raider Invasion of Mos Espa: Phase 3
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Tusken King who leads the invasion of Tusken Raiders into Mos Espa.
